data.description: Location, location, location! This 3 bed, 2 bath rambler with extra rooms (converted carport) is 1,788 sq ft on a .27 acre lot and located on a quiet Edgewood street, surrounded by nice homes. Covered patio and detached shed in backyard; along with an older pond & previous garden beds. Large driveway with RV parking. Investors, bring your toolbelt & make this home shine again! Cash only, or Rehab loan. Estate sale, offering as-is condition. Home is occupied, please do not bother tenants. Thank you.
